Text: Running from a duel is WEAK! Stand and fight!!!
Ugh... She's so annoying...
Shut up...
Do you know Zeta?

Yeah! I'm Delta! And I got business with that
scaredy cat!
You heard her. So, what'd you do?

Beats me. But hey, you're talking like you've never
met Delta before, but aren't you guys in the same
class?
Huh? Oh, um, that's right.

Well, all good if you don't remember. She's just
gonna come bite you for no reason like she is now.
It's not for no reason!!! Why'd you skip PE?!
Zeta, you can't be cutting classes.
Ahaha... Well, it's not like I can say no to you.

But now I found you, so it's, um...whatever you call
it! Game on!!!
No can do. I'm in the middle of something.
Game on!!!
Shut up... Go outside if you're gonna be so noisy...
It's on!!!
...No one's listening...
Hey, you.
What?! I'm busy! Just stay quiet and keep your noseâ€”
What?
Eep?!

Delta, was it? Would you be interested in joining
the Photography Club?

No, no, no! No way! Absolutely not!!! Let me clue
you in on just who it is we're talking about here,
Alpha!

She's a serious troublemaker who has straight F's in
everything except PE and is always in trouble with
teachers for destroying school property!

I don't see an issue. You, her, and Eta will be like
three toublemaking peas in a pod, no?
Grr! I think I smell an insult!
I'm not a problem child...
Um, from any viewpoint, you're nothing but trouble.
Anyway, I'm 100-percent deadset against it!

But it's not like we have any other candidates,
now do we?

Besides, she's got the physical skills to keep up
with you, right? It'd certainly be reassuring to
have her on our side in a fight.

...*sigh* Fine. Gotta crack a few eggs to make an
omelet, huh.
Hey! Stop saying confusing stuff! It's all nonsense!
I'll explain everything, so just listen quietly.

Ulp... Y-You're kinda scary... O-Okay. I'll keep my
mouth zipped.

â€”And so, we have to destroy the Dark Histories and
exterminate the evil spirits.
Dark pastries...? Inflate evil spirits...?

...It's no good, Alpha. She didn't understand a
word of it.

I-I did too understand! I'll fight evil spirits!
It sounds fun!
So simple-minded...

Nice to see you reacting so positively. So will you
join us?
No, I won't! Because of Zeta!
O-Oh for the love of...

I'm all for having her on the team, but it seems
like we're at a bit of a deadlock here.
Hey, Delta. You want to have duel with Zeta, right?

Yeah! And when I win, she's gonna give me a fried
noodle roll!
What if it were three fried noodle rolls instead?
Hmm? What do you mean?

You'll get your showdown with Zeta, like you want.
And if you win, Zeta, Eta, and I will buy you three
fried noodle rolls.

But if Zeta wins...then you have to join the
Photography Club.
Three fried noodle rolls! I'm in!!!

Alright, I'll be waiting at the gym! Don't even
think of trying to get outta this!
...And off she goes. What a hothead.
How did I get dragged into this...?

Gotta say, that was a jerk move, Alpha. Way to just
decide everything for yourself.
Oh, is someone not confident in her chances?

Don't be silly. I'll get that bonehead in our club,
you'll see.
